  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FROM THE GROUND-UP</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793360/extras/7fdb4e888b5d7e376e16593e7ca0a332.poster.avif?t=1651528197\" width=540 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793360/extras/7fdb4e888b5d7e376e16593e7ca0a332.webm?t=1651528197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Construct your cafe from the ground up! From the very foundation to the furniture your customers will sit on, the customization to change style and theme of your store is endless!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COFFEE CREATION</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793360/extras/9a7eaef379269b310726a98344efe934.poster.avif?t=1651528197\" width=540 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793360/extras/9a7eaef379269b310726a98344efe934.webm?t=1651528197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Carefully craft your coffee items while analyzing the expenses and profits for each drink!<br><br>Manage what kind of employees you wish to hire in order for your store to come to life!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HIRE EMPLOYEES</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793360/extras/c3ddee8eac1f5b8d074a07b5b4867f4a.poster.avif?t=1651528197\" width=700 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793360/extras/c3ddee8eac1f5b8d074a07b5b4867f4a.webm?t=1651528197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Manage your employees for each role! Each employee has their own skills, experience, and personality that would ultimately affect your customers moods! Choose carefully and manage carefully!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WISHLIST TODAY!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793360/extras/37aab5de30847d5feada6afacc46d892.avif?t=1651528197\" width=600 height=200 /></span>",
