 employee has their own skills, experience, and personality that would ultimately affect your customers moods! Choose carefully and manage carefully!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WISHLIST TODAY!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793360/extras/37aab5de30847d5feada6afacc46d892.avif?t=1651528197\" width=600 height=200 /></span>",
